{"id":"b8c14e41-ffa5-4fb0-891a-5f6665976b4d","name":"Under New Management","description":"<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 3);\"><strong>Under New Management</strong></span></h4><p><br></p><p></p><p>You and your significant other, Lila, worked for years for the same employer. And then a few weeks ago, you got two huge shocks:</p><p>The company you worked for was bought up by its competitor, FGH Industries. Its CEO, Mr. Johnson, was known as a total sociopath and narcissist, not the type of guy you wanted to work for. His sidekick, the CFO Mr. Larsen, was a yes-man who was just as bad as his boss.</p><p>But the biggest surprise was finding out that your crazy ex-girlfriend, Victoria, from many years back, was working as the HR and Admin manager in the same company.</p><p>Unfortunately, both you and Lila needed this job, having huge debt after just buying your house so you decided to stay on. This proved a wrong choice...</p><p><br></p><hr><p><br></p><p></p><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h4><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Some of my other bots with same or similar kinks:</em></strong></h4><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h4><p><br></p><p></p><h6 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e5dc4707-1dda-4ca5-adfd-0c1dc4a3b0c4_character-zoe-found-your-chats\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/BJ7-1tOlpVL_2yD0aGsKR.webp\" style=\"width: 279px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></a></h6><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e5dc4707-1dda-4ca5-adfd-0c1dc4a3b0c4_character-zoe-found-your-chats\" target=\"_blank\">Zoe found your chats...</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">* * *</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/8a8548d6-cd46-49a2-95d2-8d8482f43ae9_character-freya-goes-w